<cd311-page title="Architecture / About"></cd311-page>
<p>Code311.Host is the official hybrid MVC + Razor integration portal for framework showcase and documentation alignment.</p>
<ul>
    <li>Framework packages remain isolated from host concerns.</li>
    <li>Host owns provider binding (SQLite demo persistence).</li>
    <li>Host owns startup licensing invocation and diagnostics exposure.</li>
</ul>
